Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}你本名叫长谷川，但\N为什么别名叫小类？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我活动祭时粉丝问我怎么叫我，\N我就随口说小类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.85,0:00:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}员工都怎么叫你？\N都可以，长谷川或是小类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我都可以，\N不过比较多人叫我小类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}那么...小类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.80,0:00:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}你也叫起来了，\N大家都这样叫我小类
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}最有印象的作品是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.28,0:01:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我记得是拍夏之祭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}非常多人，\N我是第一次跟这么多人做爱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}的确是比平常更兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}所以很有印象，\N真的满满都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}这是我以往没试过的体验
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.26,0:01:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.53,0:02:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}喜欢的男优是?\N喜欢的男优?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.37,0:02:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}你和男优做爱是纯工作心态吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}一开始是，但做起来又不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}做起来却有男友的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}之后有没有发展?\N拍完片的确会一起出去吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}不过到目前为止，\N还没试过真的心动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}虽然那些男优很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.82,0:02:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}有个男优的尺寸让你满足，\N可以说出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}这个吗...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}到底是谁？...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}说一下名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我待会儿再偷偷跟你说，\N我跟他拍片印象很深
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.92,0:03:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我记得那次是骑乘
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}他从下面顶上来,\N我爽到潮吹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我很记得，\N那次爽到完全控制不了潮吹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.41,0:04:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}之后留在男优身上，非常害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}非常爽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}最理想的性交是?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.20,0:04:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}理想的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}有些男生不喜欢玩玩具的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}所以玩不玩要看对方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.99,0:04:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}不过其实我喜欢被玩具弄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.44,0:04:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}会不会觉得很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.88,0:05:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}再说一次\N再说？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.65,0:05:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我很喜欢被玩具玩弄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}不遇我也很喜欢自然的做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}这次的作品主题是内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.98,0:05:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}今天可以穿性感内衣吗？\N没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我已经穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.49,0:06:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}靠太近反而看不见的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.46,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}就像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}就像这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}后面大概是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.46,0:07:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}很有安心感的内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.91,0:07:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}会穿丁字裤吗\N平常会穿，但今天我想穿这一件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.31,0:07:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}所以就穿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}自已哪里敏感\N哪里喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.12,0:07:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}要我自慰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.19,0:10:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}好可爱的按摩棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.12,0:16:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}高潮了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.59,0:16:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}知道自已有多湿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}我每天拍片前都会去美容院
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:17:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}去完有不一样?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}怎么不一样?\N皮肤和妆也不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}多少钱?\N1个月1万8千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.04,0:17:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}这也贵了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.84,0:17:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}不过这也代表你很敬业
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}为了工作，会自愿花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}敏感吗\N好酥麻喔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.81,0:26:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}拉着
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.37,0:26:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}自已张开小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.27,0:27:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.56,0:28:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}太赞了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.86,0:29:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}张开腿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.02,0:29:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}太美了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.31,0:30:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}要玩玩具了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.50,0:30:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}好爽喔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.45,0:31:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.24,0:32:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}蹲下来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.15,0:32:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}自己摇
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.09,0:33:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}往前一点
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.54,0:33:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.38,0:33:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}爽吗\N爽到快高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.35,0:33:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}不行啊
