Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.02,0:35:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.64,0:36:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.28,0:39:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}想要吗？\N想要了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.59,0:39:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}快干我\N下面想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.35,0:39:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}插这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.69,0:39:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}快进来...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.33,0:39:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.90,0:39:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}顶的好深喔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.40,0:40:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}再用力点
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.01,0:40:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}爽死我了，用力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.14,0:40:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}受不了了，去了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.51,0:41:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs18\shad3\4a&H80&}继续干我啊
